'''乳香树'''<ref>{{Cite web|title=橄榄科 Burseraceae（中国植物志）|url=http://www.iplant.cn/info/Burseraceae?t=z|accessdate=2020-09-19|work=iPlant.cn 植物智——中国植物物种信息系统|publisher=中国科学院植物研究所系统与进化植物学国家重点实验室}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=''Boswellia carterii'' Birdw.; ''B. sacra'' Fluck. - 乳香樹|url=http://terms.naer.edu.tw/detail/574700/?index=5|accessdate=2020-09-19|work=雙語詞彙、學術名詞暨辭書資訊網|publisher=國家教育研究院}}</ref>（{{lang-xm|Boswellia sacra}}，学名的意思是'''神圣乳香'''）為[[乳香屬|乳香屬]]下的一種植物，其[[樹脂|樹脂]]凝固後便成[[乳香|乳香]]。

编写《索马里植物志》的植物学家马茨·图林（{{lang|sv|Mats Thulin}}）把原产[[阿曼|阿曼]]和[[也门|也门]]的'''-{阿拉伯}-乳香树'''（{{lang-xm|Boswellia sacra}}）和原产[[索马里|索马里]]的'''索马里乳香树'''（{{lang-xm|Boswellia carteri}}）合为一种，后者作为前者的异名。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=The frankincense trees (''Boswellia'' spp., Burseraceae) of northern Somalia and southern Arabia|url=https://www.jstor.org/stable/4110063|last=Thulin|first=M.|last2=Warfa|first2=A. M.|date=1987|journal=Kew Bulletin|issue=3|doi=10.2307/4110063|volume=42|pages=487–500|issn=0075-5974|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2021-07-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210716094331/https://www.jstor.org/stable/4110063|dead-url=no}}</ref>但亦有学者根据乳香化学成分差异认为二者是两个不同的物种。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Chemical differentiation of ''Boswellia sacra'' and ''Boswellia carterii'' essential oils by gas chromatography and chiral gas chromatography–mass spectrometry|url=https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0021967312009673|last=Woolley|first=Cole L.|last2=Suhail|first2=Mahmoud M.|date=2012-10-26|journal=Journal of Chromatography A|doi=10.1016/j.chroma.2012.06.073|series=High Speed and High Resolution Separations. In Honour of Professor Milton Lee on the Occasion of his 65th Birthday|volume=1261|pages=158–163|issn=0021-9673|last3=Smith|first3=Brett L.|last4=Boren|first4=Karen E.|last5=Taylor|first5=Lindsey C.|last6=Schreuder|first6=Marc F.|last7=Chai|first7=Jeremiah K.|last8=Casabianca|first8=Hervé|last9=Haq|first9=Sadqa|access-date=2021-02-27|archive-date=2017-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170510184702/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0021967312009673|dead-url=no}}</ref>

